videos.description: With Baylor running the fast break, Texas' Kerwin Roach Jr. flies in from behind to make a huge block against the backboard to deny the Bears a basket.
videos.headline: Roach flies in for block out of nowhere

videos.description: Baylor turned an eight point lead into an 11 point advantage at the half with Jake Lindsey's 3-pointer from the corner to beat the first half buzzer.
videos.headline: Lindsey ends the half with buzzer-beater for Baylor

videos.description: While his teammates miss three times at the rim, Baylor's Ishmail Wainwright flies in for the huge one-hand to punctuate the Bears' win over Texas.
videos.headline: Wainwright finishes off Texas with monster dunk
